{
  "texts": [
    "In both cases, the answer has a well-established structure: beginning, main part and conclusion.",
    "Chatbot also includes into the description words from a prompt.",
    "For example, if the request contains the words \"joy\" and \"pleasure\" the result will be: The world seemed to radiate with pure joy and boundless pleasure.",
    "In most cases, ChatGPT generates exceptional descriptions of places that could be used in human-written texts.",
    "However, the chatbot uses too many stylistic devices within one sentence, which makes the output overwhelming."
  ]
}